  "text": "It is important to observe that Rocketfuel ISP topologies are subject to inference errors. In particular, [CITATION_1] demonstrates that the inclusion of links that do not exist and the omission of links that are actually present can inflate path diversity in these inferred topologies. This limits the accuracy of node arities computed above.",
